      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Wolfgang.AuditTrail.AuditOperation",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.AuditTrail.AuditOperation.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Identifies the type of change captured on an <xref href=\"Wolfgang.AuditTrail.Entities.AuditHeader\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> row.\nThe underlying byte values are the ASCII codes for <code>'I'</code>, <code>'U'</code>, and <code>'D'</code>;\nthe EF model converts the enum through <code>char</code> on the way out so the database\ncolumn literally contains <code>'I'</code> / <code>'U'</code> / <code>'D'</code> when queried directly.</p>\n"
    },
    {
