      "Title": "Wolfgang.AuditTrail.AuditSaveChangesInterceptor",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.AuditTrail.AuditSaveChangesInterceptor.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Auto-transaction <xref href=\"Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Diagnostics.ISaveChangesInterceptor\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> that captures Insert /\nUpdate / Delete operations via <xref href=\"Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.DbContext.ChangeTracker\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> and writes\naudit header + detail rows in the same transaction as the user's save.</p>\n"
    },
